General.Name: N Brown Group PLC
General.Description: N Brown Group plc operates as a clothing and footwear digital retailer in the United Kingdom. The company offers a range of clothing, footwear, and homeware products for men and women under the JD Williams, Simply Be, Ambrose Wilson, Jacamo, Home Essentials, Fashion World, Marisota, Oxendales, and Premier Man brands. It also provides financial services. The company was founded in 1859 and is headquartered in Manchester, the United Kingdom.
General.Address: Griffin House, Manchester, United Kingdom, M60 6ES
